text: Covey usually refers to group of certain birds such as partridges or quails. Covey may also refer to: * Covey (surname) ==See also== * FranklinCovey, provider of business education and training based on Stephen Covey's writings * Smith's Ballpark, Utah baseball stadium formerly known as Franklin Covey Field * 20th Tactical Air Support Squadron used Covey as its call sign during the Vietnam War (Second Indochina War)
title: Covey (disambiguation)
